{
  "text": "Bleeding from stomal varices has been reported in up to 20% of the patients suffering with chronic liver failure with permanent stoma [CITATION_1] . However, the diagnosis of stomal varices is difficult because bleeding from stoma may also be associated with lower gastrointestinal bleeding.",
